%t A119275 Table[(-1)^(n - k) (n - k)!*Binomial[n + 1, k + 1] Binomial[k + 1, n - k], {n, 0, 10}, {k, 0, n}] // Flatten (* _Michael De Vlieger_, Oct 12 2016 *)
%t A119275 BellMatrix[f_Function, len_] := With[{t = Array[f, len, 0]}, Table[BellY[n, k, t], {n, 0, len - 1}, {k, 0, len - 1}]];
